{"tid":506384,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"生緊智障齒 應該點做","createTime":"2017-12-22T07:03:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-22T10:51:20.000Z","uid":36104,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"28cfb3edb738d467a234f09ec28f5bff49273caf","tid":506384,"uid":36104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T07:03:59.000Z","msg":"生緊智障齒<br />\n痛到媽媽都唔認得<br />\n可以點做<br />\n<br />\nBtw 上齶兩隻好似生完，唔係幾夠位，出得一半，唔痛<br />\n<br />\n下面右邊之前又係勁痛<br />\n凌晨去排睇公立牙醫，話發炎定未生好唔可以剝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 排兩年期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我冇去到，因為已經冇事<br />\n但之後刷牙刷得唔好蛀左，又冇神經，好深先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後用自己part time 錢喺大學診所剝左，千幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家到左邊下面又係好痛<br />\n剝就冇得剝，但有冇得舒緩下，好撚痛呀屌佢老母智障齒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e8dc1d001c1ebee60a16e6089a23726129de77","tid":506384,"uid":36104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T07:05:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"475c00395fb27c63ecd38aa09bdf1003a96a4940","tid":506384,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T07:06:32.000Z","msg":"千幾蚊咪算平囉"},{"pid":"4482cc2e65125967e0bf5c39588173fbec6fe383","tid":506384,"uid":36104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T07:15:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>千幾蚊咪算平囉</blockquote><br />\n學生冇錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我番pt搵幾多食幾多<br />\n係有正苦生活費先有錢剝"},{"pid":"6f6c7c9803f6875fbac823b96d6b4e26911409a4","tid":506384,"uid":145247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T07:20:58.000Z","msg":"準備定身後事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c462d05bb377e45b05a0c92914699b7941d306c","tid":506384,"uid":36104,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T07:22:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>準備定身後事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好笑咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登咁撚多你呢啲小學雞真係白撚痴"},{"pid":"6d2e2fa5338a02e49943191ff1fe37dce44cf557","tid":506384,"uid":36087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T07:46:15.000Z","msg":"智障齒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a8bcb568e01a23d392e62cac6674ffcb719cefd","tid":506384,"uid":86717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T07:47:43.000Z","msg":"比錢啦 我要比5千幾仲肉痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4623ef7cc401648447e1e507b8b03f17e5c4a8","tid":506384,"uid":36104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T08:32:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比錢啦 我要比5千幾仲肉痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n生緊唔剝得<br />\n有錢都冇用<br />\n況且冇錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa4be3e59a38db5486eb7f5b4af2c87271d91537","tid":506384,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T08:42:22.000Z","msg":"其實唔痛就唔洗理佢 平時刷牙刷入啲就得"},{"pid":"908022b81caf2409f0d0e73f3837bdf71e91d042","tid":506384,"uid":36045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T08:50:32.000Z","msg":"俾錢<br />\n不過下顎無病無痛好少剝<br />\n始終都近神經線"},{"pid":"9de9e5ec562f39d0b63a629cff50c05e26753df4","tid":506384,"uid":79182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T09:00:09.000Z","msg":"下個月剝<br />\n三千<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aefd81c8a692973f123ba67516e88fb57ff629c7","tid":506384,"uid":1928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T09:01:45.000Z","msg":"咬爛個邊d牙肉"},{"pid":"7d781e052d768f86707f12047f182cdb33f4dcb6","tid":506384,"uid":160791,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T09:05:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f4935586149da32e7b7abdb11199a7e2468ed3e","tid":506384,"uid":162644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T09:07:19.000Z","msg":"要平可以去排菲臘牙科，<br />\n我前年都係個邊剝，原本得一隻痛諗住剝一隻<br />\n點知照x光原來生哂4隻，一隻突緊出黎3隻打橫生<br />\n醫生建議我一獲過做哂4隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n剝完住埋院500唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290130d8f7156736927a32a7dac23714f5e10c49","tid":506384,"uid":107571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T09:18:09.000Z","msg":"如果隻智慧齒出到黎<br />\n特別係上顎可以去政府牙科街症剝<br />\n唔洗錢仲好快手 個牙醫見你隻牙出得曬會建議你切牙冠<br />\n下顎唔夠位出就要去搵私家牙醫剝<br />\n私家自己google邊幾位個朵好 <br />\n打個電話約閒日幾日內照x光幫你剝 真係複雜case個牙醫會轉介<br />\n<br />\n始終剝智慧齒算手術 特別下顎近3叉神經線 貴少少好正常<br />\n <br />\n利申：4隻剝左3隻 上顎排街症 下顎兩隻開刀 其中一隻磨左少少牙槽骨先出到 另一隻近3叉神經 麻醉左剝個陣都feel到力"},{"pid":"eb75e52b3b16bb0bccc896482b551d3590eb40fa","tid":506384,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T09:29:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>比錢啦 我要比5千幾仲肉痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n生緊唔剝得<br />\n有錢都冇用<br />\n況且冇錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果太接近神經線，你有錢都唔幫你剝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"cb30be500f76c8fec2c1d2ebff3ed83febeb779c","tid":506384,"uid":36104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T09:44:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多齒症<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://s3-us-west-1.amazonaws.com/niusnews-imgs/144448_7.mg]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-us-west-1.amazonaws.com%2Fniusnews-imgs%2F144448_7.mg%5D&d=LX3jfKltR5G0quaevRKfHAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=9736932f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s3-us-west-1.amazonaws.com/niusnews-imgs/144448_7.mg]</a></blockquote><br />\n咪弱智啦<br />\n你老母生到你咁痴線做咩唔睇醫生"},{"pid":"88e89631d79bb0b6ff3e0ec05e15500783d091cb","tid":506384,"uid":36104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T09:46:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>比錢啦 我要比5千幾仲肉痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n生緊唔剝得<br />\n有錢都冇用<br />\n況且冇錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果太接近神經線，你有錢都唔幫你剝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</blockquote><br />\n唔係嘅<br />\n上次剝右邊佢幫我照過睇神經線<br />\n佢話掂住就會有風險冇曬肌肉控制能力<br />\n但我係啱啱好冇掂倒，風險好低<br />\n其實唔蛀都唔剝啦<br />\n隻牙有感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e287ad12a147f18424edae8c5623075974da91","tid":506384,"uid":36104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T09:49:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果隻智慧齒出到黎<br />\n特別係上顎可以去政府牙科街症剝<br />\n唔洗錢仲好快手 個牙醫見你隻牙出得曬會建議你切牙冠<br />\n下顎唔夠位出就要去搵私家牙醫剝<br />\n私家自己google邊幾位個朵好 <br />\n打個電話約閒日幾日內照x光幫你剝 真係複雜case個牙醫會轉介<br />\n<br />\n始終剝智慧齒算手術 特別下顎近3叉神經線 貴少少好正常<br />\n <br />\n利申：4隻剝左3隻 上顎排街症 下顎兩隻開刀 其中一隻磨左少少牙槽骨先出到 另一隻近3叉神經 麻醉左剝個陣都feel到力</blockquote><br />\n係呀，就係算手術又要麻醉，所以先咁貴姐應該<br />\n佢又唔肯幫我補<br />\n我估因為補平好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋咁入又麻煩<br />\n<br />\n不過學校診所都估唔到幾好手勢<br />\n除左錢都冇乜問題"},{"pid":"987d252bb5d3f1ca2eb31aa8bb9ae335e72b8b99","tid":506384,"uid":36104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T09:50:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實唔痛就唔洗理佢 平時刷牙刷入啲就得</blockquote><br />\n一路刷一路痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但為左唔會蛀，都係日日刷兩次，重要重點刷𠴱隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1724e027dc245a0086c14179b8f9f51c06c82832","tid":506384,"uid":36104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T09:52:28.000Z","msg":"有冇方法可以舒緩下，痛到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見倒腫腫地"},{"pid":"05ede12a1afda1166d9271311540fcbfa601f19e","tid":506384,"uid":155067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T09:54:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇方法可以舒緩下，痛到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見倒腫腫地</blockquote><br />\n痛博士。好貴下<br />\n之後買成葯<br />\n買消炎止痛<br />\n再去睇牙醫book定睇幾時剝得"},{"pid":"27e4930203f4db22325a0420a187c5dd1c37d5eb","tid":506384,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T09:54:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要平可以去排菲臘牙科，<br />\n我前年都係個邊剝，原本得一隻痛諗住剝一隻<br />\n點知照x光原來生哂4隻，一隻突緊出黎3隻打橫生<br />\n醫生建議我一獲過做哂4隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n剝完住埋院500唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要排幾耐 我暑假開始排緊"},{"pid":"24d14af5641c9c197738922928e0bd05d583fcae","tid":506384,"uid":54550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T09:56:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比錢啦 我要比5千幾仲肉痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我個醫生同我講四千一隻，你有三隻。面色一沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要補多刀，我係你呢就KO晒啲蛀牙先，有錢先慢慢逐隻剝，反正都係要剝，無得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}